longBusinessSummary: Bonava AB (publ) operates as a residential developer in Germany, Sweden, Finland, Norway, Estonia, Latvia, and Lithuania. The company constructs multi-family and single-family housing units. It also develops homes for consumers and investors, such as pension funds, municipalities, and other stakeholders. Bonava AB (publ) was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
